platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: In search of a dog walker or pet sitter? Rover connects you with trustworthy sitters who give your animals the care they deserve. We’ve used the app to find locals to watch our cat while we’re away and walk our dogs when we can’t. We’d say it’s doggone amazing.
Connect with trustworthy dog walkers and pet sitters who will watch your cat while you’re away, or walk your dog when you can’t–and above all give your animals the care they deserve.
Trouvez quelqu’un de confiance pour garder votre chat ou promener votre chien en votre absence. Donnez à vos animaux l’attention qu’ils méritent.
